He seemed ordinary like other children. But who knew he would grow up to save the universe at it's darkest phase in history. The boy would
save everyone...this boy who is imbued with the power and strength of a Titan. In 10 years he would lead the entire world to fight a glorious war...the war between man and machine. We would
eventually win but at the cost of millions of lives, including this saviour who made the ultimate sacrifice in order to wipe out the machines into oblivion once and for all
